description: Work to trace any new strain starts, and non-essential shops "likely" to stay shut until 11 January.
title: Covid: New coronavirus strain 'likely to be in Jersey'
title_page: Covid: New coronavirus strain 'likely to be in Jersey' - BBC News
maintext: At a press conference, Senator Le Fondre said: "We are already taking steps to establish if that new strain is present in our community, and it is likely that it is present in our island.
